{%- comment -%}
  Collapsible content — accordéon Q/R universel (FAQ).

  Section UNIQUE du theme pour tous les usages accordion :
  - Home FAQ (templates/index.json)
  - Pages produit (product.painting.json, product.json, etc.)
  - Pages articles (article.*.json)

  Conventions skill shopify-section-dev :
  - Tailwind only (aucun CSS scoped)
  - Variables globales : font-heading, font-roboto, text-main, text-main-90,
    text-terra, bg-main-10, bg-terra, bg-secondary, border-main-10
  - REUSE FIRST : <collapsible-tab> custom element ([assets/tw-global.js])
    qui gère single-open + click body to close + link bail-out.
  - Admin-configurable strict
  - SEO : <h2>/<h3> configurable, aria-labelledby, JSON-LD FAQPage dynamique
  - A11y : <details>/<summary> natifs, motion-reduce, focus-visible:ring,
    aria-hidden sur icon

  Visuel issu de l'ancien home-faq (validé Walid) — reprend 1:1 le design
  original CSS scoped (assets/home-styles.css lignes 487-562) en Tailwind.

  COMPATIBILITÉ ASCENDANTE :
  - Block type `collapsible_row` conservé (préserve les 65 blocks existants
    répartis sur 10 templates produits/articles).
  - Settings block : `heading` (text), `row_content` (richtext), `icon` (select)
    inchangés. Le `icon` est conservé en schema pour data-compat mais non rendu
    visuellement (le nouveau design utilise le "+" rond plus minimaliste).
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign heading_level = section.settings.heading_level | default: 'h2'
  assign heading_id = 'collapsible-' | append: section.id
  assign show_header = false
  if section.settings.eyebrow != blank or section.settings.heading != blank or section.settings.lead != blank
    assign show_header = true
  endif

  case section.settings.background_color
    when 'cream'
      assign bg_class = 'bg-main-5'
    when 'sable'
      assign bg_class = 'bg-main-10'
    when 'transparent'
      assign bg_class = ''
    else
      assign bg_class = 'bg-secondary'
  endcase

  case section.settings.padding_size
    when 'small'
      assign pad_class = 'py-10 md:py-14'
    when 'medium'
      assign pad_class = 'py-14 md:py-20'
    else
      assign pad_class = 'py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-[120px]'
  endcase

  case section.settings.heading_size
    when 'small'
      assign heading_size_class = 'text-xl md:text-2xl'
    when 'large'
      assign heading_size_class = 'text-[32px] md:text-[44px] lg:text-[56px]'
    else
      assign heading_size_class = 'text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-[36px]'
  endcase

  case section.settings.heading_weight
    when 'light'
      assign heading_weight_class = 'font-light'
    when 'normal'
      assign heading_weight_class = 'font-normal'
    when 'medium'
      assign heading_weight_class = 'font-medium'
    when 'bold'
      assign heading_weight_class = 'font-bold'
    else
      assign heading_weight_class = 'font-semibold'
  endcase

  case section.settings.question_size
    when 'small'
      assign question_size_class = 'text-[15px] md:text-base'
    when 'large'
      assign question_size_class = 'text-[18px] md:text-[22px]'
    else
      assign question_size_class = 'text-base md:text-lg'
  endcase

  comment
    accent_tone — pilote la couleur de l'icon ouvert + des liens.
    Trois tons disponibles, tous dérivés du brand_color global (admin) :
    - terra (brand-700, par défaut)        : terracotta foncé saturé (home)
    - buy-button (brand-500)               : même couleur que le bouton Panier/Buy
    - brand-900                            : terracotta très sombre (chocolat)
    On garde la couleur de brand globale, on règle juste la TONALITÉ ici.
  endcomment
  case section.settings.accent_tone
    when 'buy-button'
      assign accent_bg_class = 'group-open:bg-buy-button'
      assign accent_icon_open_class = 'group-open:text-main'
      assign accent_link_class = '[&_a]:text-buy-button'
    when 'brand-900'
      assign accent_bg_class = 'group-open:bg-brand-900'
      assign accent_icon_open_class = 'group-open:text-secondary'
      assign accent_link_class = '[&_a]:text-brand-900'
    else
      assign accent_bg_class = 'group-open:bg-terra'
      assign accent_icon_open_class = 'group-open:text-secondary'
      assign accent_link_class = '[&_a]:text-terra'
  endcase
-%}

<section
  class="collapsible-content {{ bg_class }} text-main w-full {{ pad_class }}"
  {% if show_header %}aria-labelledby="{{ heading_id }}"{% endif %}>

  {%- comment -%} Header centré, max 760px (cohérent avec home-faq) {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if show_header -%}
    <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-10 md:mb-16">

      {%- if section.settings.eyebrow != blank -%}
        <p class="font-roboto text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-terra mb-4">
          {{ section.settings.eyebrow | escape }}
        </p>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.heading != blank -%}
        <{{ heading_level }}
          id="{{ heading_id }}"
          class="font-heading {{ heading_weight_class }} leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.01em] {{ heading_size_class }} mb-6">
          {{ section.settings.heading | escape }}
        </{{ heading_level }}>
      {%- endif -%}

      {%- if section.settings.lead != blank -%}
        <p class="font-roboto text-base md:text-lg lg:text-[19px] leading-[1.65] text-main-70 mb-0">
          {{ section.settings.lead }}
        </p>
      {%- endif -%}

    </div>
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- comment -%} Liste, max 880px, padding 24px (visuel original Walid) {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- if section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
    <collapsible-tab>
      <div class="max-w-[880px] mx-auto px-6">
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type == 'collapsible_row' -%}
            <details
              class="accordion group border-t border-main-10 last:border-b last:border-main-10"
              {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>

              {%- comment -%}
                Summary flex justify-between, py-6, gap-6, cursor-pointer.
                focus-visible:ring-2 ring-terra pour a11y clavier (l'outline
                default est retiré par list-none — on remet un focus ring).
              {%- endcomment -%}
              <summary class="list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden cursor-pointer flex items-center justify-between gap-6 py-6 outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-terra focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:rounded-sm">
                <h3 class="font-heading font-medium leading-[1.3] {{ question_size_class }} text-main m-0">
                  {{ block.settings.heading | escape }}
                </h3>
                {%- comment -%}
                  Icon "+" — rond 32×32 fond sable au repos.
                  Quand <details open> : fond terra (brand-700 plein),
                  texte blanc, rotation 45° → "×". Transition douce.
                {%- endcomment -%}
                <span
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-main-10 text-main flex items-center justify-center text-[20px] leading-none transition-[background-color,transform] duration-300 ease-out motion-reduce:transition-none {{ accent_bg_class }} {{ accent_icon_open_class }} group-open:rotate-45">
                  +
                </span>
              </summary>

              {%- comment -%}
                Réponse — font-sans 15px, leading 1.7, text-main-90 (sombre lisible).
                p:not(:last-child) mb-3 (=12px). Liens text-terra underline.
                Strong text-main + font-semibold.
                cursor-pointer rappelle au lecteur que le body est cliquable.
              {%- endcomment -%}
              <div class="pb-7 max-w-[760px] cursor-pointer">
                <div class="font-roboto text-[15px] leading-[1.7] text-main-90 [&>p:not(:last-child)]:mb-3 {{ accent_link_class }} [&_a]:underline [&_a:hover]:opacity-80 motion-reduce:[&_a]:transition-none [&_strong]:text-main [&_strong]:font-semibold">
                  {{ block.settings.row_content }}
                </div>
              </div>

            </details>
          {%- endif -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      </div>
    </collapsible-tab>

    <script src="{{ 'tw-global.js' | asset_url }}" defer="defer"></script>
  {%- endif -%}

</section>

{%- comment -%}
  JSON-LD FAQPage dynamique — depuis les blocks (source de vérité unique).
  Activable depuis le schema (emit_faq_jsonld) : à n'activer que sur les pages
  où l'accordéon EST bien une FAQ (page home, page FAQ dédiée). Pas sur les
  pages produit où les blocks parlent de matière/livraison du produit (et où
  Shopify émet déjà du JSON-LD Product).
{%- endcomment -%}
{%- if section.settings.emit_faq_jsonld and section.blocks.size > 0 -%}
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {%- assign emitted = 0 -%}
        {%- for block in section.blocks -%}
          {%- if block.type != 'collapsible_row' -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}
          {%- if block.settings.heading == blank or block.settings.row_content == blank -%}{%- continue -%}{%- endif -%}
          {%- if emitted > 0 -%},{%- endif -%}
          {%- liquid
            assign answer_text = block.settings.row_content | strip_html | strip | replace: '"', '\"'
          -%}
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": {{ block.settings.heading | json }},
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": {{ answer_text | json }}
            }
          }
          {%- assign emitted = emitted | plus: 1 -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      ]
    }
  </script>
{%- endif -%}

